verses.roman:
madhya-līlā-madhye antya-līlā-sūtra-gaṇa
pūrva-granthe saṅkṣepete kariyāchi varṇana

synonyms: madhya-līlā-madhye—within the madhya-līlā chapters; antya-līlā-sūtra-gaṇa—a synopsis of the antya-līlā; pūrva-granthe—in the previous chapter; saṅkṣepete—in brief; kariyāchi varṇana—I have described.
translation: I have briefly described the antya-līlā within the description of the madhya-līlā.
